---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="System Integration & Tooling - intelio">
<main>
  <!-- HERO SECTION (Dark) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-normal mb-4 sm:mb-6">System Integration & Tooling</h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-400">Connecting CRMs, accounting, operations, and data into one coordinated system.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: What Breaks (Light) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-white text-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8">What Breaks</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Most businesses already own good tools—they just don't work together.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: What We Do (Dark) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8">What We Do</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">We integrate, automate, and simplify your existing stack:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>CRMs</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Accounting systems</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Operations tools</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Data platforms</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">The result is a coordinated system instead of disconnected software.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA SECTION (Light) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-white text-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-8 sm:mb-12">Ready to connect your tools?</h2>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-black text-white text-base sm:text-lg font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors min-h-[56px]">
        Work with Intelio
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</Layout>

